---
import Head from "../../components/Head.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<html>
  <Head title="Tire Calligraphy - Dobokh Parkha" url="https://tirecalli.com/Dobokh-Parkha" />
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <article class="product">
        <aside class="product__aside">
          <div class="product__figures">
            <a href="details.html#photo-1"><img src="/img/Dobokh-Parkha/girl-in-black-jacket-front.webp" alt="Girl in black Dobokh Parka" /></a>
            <a href="details.html#photo-2"><img src="/img/Dobokh-Parkha/girl-in-black-jacket-short-slevees-front.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" /></a>
          </div>
          <div class="product__figures">
            <a href="details.html#photo-3"
              ><img src="/img/Dobokh-Parkha/girl-in-black-jacket-side-sleeves-hanging.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            <a href="details.html#photo-4"><img src="/img/Dobokh-Parkha/girl-in-black-jacket-side.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" loading="lazy" /></a>
          </div>
          <div class="product__figures">
            <a href="details.html#photo-5"><img src="/img/Dobokh-Parkha/girl-with-jacket-on-shoulder-front.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" loading="lazy" /></a>
            <a href="details.html#photo-6"
              ><img src="/img/Dobokh-Parkha/tire-calligraphy-black-parka-jacket-letters.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="product__figures">
            <a href="details.html#photo-7"><img src="/img/Dobokh-Parkha/man-in-black-jacket-front.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" loading="lazy" /></a>
            <a href="details.html#photo-8"><img src="/img/Dobokh-Parkha/man-in-black-jacket-side.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" loading="lazy" /></a>
          </div>
          <div class="product__figures">
            <a href="details.html#photo-9"
              ><img src="/img/Dobokh-Parkha/man-in-black-jacket-back-tire-calligraphy.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            <div></div>
          </div>
        </aside>
        <section class="product__info">
          <div class="product__item">
            <h2>DOBOKH PARKHA</h2>
            <h2>199144</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--price">
            <p>Price: 200€</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--size-select">
            <p>SOLD OUT</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--sizing-chart">
            <div class="btn-area">
              <label class="btn" for="open-pop">Sizing Chart</label>
            </div>
            <div class="pop-area">
              <input class="modal-state" id="open-pop" type="checkbox" />
              <div class="modal">
                <label class="modal_bg" for="open-pop"></label>
                <div class="modal_inner">
                  <label class="modal_close" for="open-pop"></label>
                  <table>
                    <tr>
                      <th colspan="3">Dobokh Parka</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td>cm / in</td>
                      <td>XS / S</td>
                      <td>S / M</td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                      <td class="label">Shoulder</td>
                      <td>59 / 23.2</td>
                      <td>63 / 24.8</td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                      <td class="label">Body</td>
                      <td>55 / 21.7</td>
                      <td>67 / 23.4</td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                      <td class="label">Length</td>
                      <td>80 / 31.5</td>
                      <td>82 / 32.3</td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--description">
            <p>
              The most complex item from the TC21 / 199144 offering. From the simplicity of a minimal black jacket, it allows you to develop your style
              depending on your own, and the current mood of the weather. Unzipping the sleeves halfway, allows you additional breathability, while removing
              them enables additional wearing technique to emerge. Adjusting the belt strap lets you play with the symmetry of the front side, which is most
              times in sight. When you need to layer down, the belt strap lets you easily carry the jacket to your destination. This one will serve you
              throughout the entire year in the warm to transitional chilly periods. Featuring an oversized hood for your protection against the elements, it
              also perfectly encapsules the hood from your inner layer.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--accordion">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div>
                <input type="checkbox" name="panel" id="panel-1" />
                <label for="panel-1">Details</label>
                <div class="accordion__content accordion__content--panel-1">
                  <ul class="accordion__list accordion-panel-1__list">
                    <li>A gender-neutral cut</li>
                    <li>5 pocket design: 1 small zippered, 2 big buttoned + 2 side pockets</li>
                    <li>Removable, zippered sleeves</li>
                    <li>Easy to carry, adjustable strap</li>
                    <li>Color: Black</li>
                    <li>Material: 100% Twill cotton (450 g, 15.87oz)</li>
                    <li>Care: Machine-wash cold, warm (30°C)</li>
                    <li>Proudly created in Croatia from local craftswomen and men</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--accordion">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div>
                <input type="checkbox" name="panel" id="panel-2" />
                <label for="panel-2">Size & Fit</label>
                <div class="accordion__content accordion__content--panel-2">
                  <ul class="accordion__list accordion-panel-2__list">
                    <li>Lana is wearing size S/M and is 175cm/5.75 ft tall</li>
                    <li>Ivan is wearing L/XL and is 187cm /6.13 ft tall</li>
                    <li>Relaxed, looser fit, you can size up or size down</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--accordion">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div>
                <input type="checkbox" name="panel" id="panel-3" />
                <label for="panel-3">Shipping & Returns</label>
                <div class="accordion__content accordion__content--panel-3">
                  <div class="accordion__copy">
                    <p class="accordion__body">Standard shipping and 30-day returns.</p>
                    <p class="accordion__body">Return policy exclusions apply.</p>
                    <p class="accordion__body">
                      <a href="/legal">Learn more.</a>
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </article>
      <section class="explore">
        <h2>Explore the Dobokh Parkha</h2>
        <p class="explore__copy">A simplicity of a minimal black jacket.</p>
        <p class="explore__copy">Adjusting the belt strap lets you play with the symmetry of the front side.</p>
        <p class="explore__copy">Unzipping the sleeves enables additional wearing technique to emerge.</p>
        <div class="explore__group">
          <div class="explore__item">
            <img src="/img/campaign/black-dobokh-parka-with-hood-mens-front.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="explore__item">
            <p class="explore__copy--middle">
              Following the postulate of fluidity and flexibility the intention was set to create items which can be used for more than one purpose and
              situation.
            </p>
            <p class="explore__copy--middle">
              With a vision of neutral, universal items in mind,
              <span class="bold">199144</span> will spread through the seasons not constrained by time, location or fashion trends.
            </p>
            <p class="explore__copy--middle">Every item offered is a neutral gender item.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="explore__item">
            <img src="/img/campaign/girl-in-black-dobokh-parkha-back.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
    <script is:inline src="/js/app.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
